Package ch.swissqr.content

Class ContentBarcodeCH

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.swissqr.content.ContentBarcodeCH
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContent
    public class ContentBarcodeCH
extends java.lang.Object
implements IContent
    Payload Information which is needed to generate a Swiss QR barcode. We provide the the functionality to construct a payload and validate the provided input. See https://www.paymentstandards.ch/dam/downloads/ig-qr-bill-en.pdf Please note that the content must be rendered in UTF-8
    Author:
    pschatzmann
